Since then, the former 007 native to Leningrad and who had served in Dresden in the Ddr>, has never in fact left the leadership of Russia and its voters recognize him the conquered political stability, economic growth, a more widespread well-being and the found posture of great power. Although all at the price of ever less freedom.
